  "prompt": "How is IIM Vishakapatnam doing with regard to exposure and placements. Is it better than IMI Delhi?",
  "response": "As of my last knowledge update in October 2023, IIM Vishakhapatnam has been steadily improving in terms of exposure, curriculum, and placement opportunities since its inception. It is part of the prestigious Indian Institutes of Management (IIM) network and benefits from the brand value and resources that come with it. The institute has been working to establish strong industry connections, facilitate internships, and enhance its overall visibility in the academic and corporate landscapes.\n\nRegarding placements, IIM Vishakhapatnam has shown promising results in recent years, with increasing numbers of companies participating in its placement processes and offering competitive packages to graduates. However, the exact placement statistics, average salary figures, and highest packages can vary each year, so it's essential to refer to the latest reports directly from the institution for the most accurate information.\n\nOn the other hand, IMI Delhi (International Management Institute) is a well-established institution with a strong reputation and has been around for a longer period. IMI Delhi has solid industry connections, diverse student exchange programs, and robust placement records. It typically attracts a range of recruiters and offers a wide array of opportunities to its students.\n\nIn terms of comparing the two, while IIM Vishakhapatnam has been growing rapidly, IMI Delhi may still hold an edge in terms of its established network, brand recognition, and alumni support. Ultimately, the choice between the two would depend on specific career goals, the preferred specialization, and individual preferences regarding campus culture and learning environment.\n\nFor the most accurate and detailed comparative insights between IIM Vishakhapatnam and IMI Delhi in terms of placements, prospective students should check the latest statistics, placement reports, and feedback from alumni.",
